person.bio: Sashi is shaping the future of consumer data in an open data economy. He enjoys building, transforming and growing new organizations, solutions and markets. Sashi believes in not only being good at what you do but by being GOOD to others, learning from the past, planning for the future while living in the PRESENT and being thoughtful about the FUTURE.
